width=30%> [[Go on the website]] She really loves the style of Frida Kahlo, the subjects and the colors...so she decides to deepen the artist by searching on the internet some of her works. [[By searching...]]Sofia is an activist for animal rights, and try to make the difference in everything she does; this could be an interesting occasion to talk about it. She decides to found her study on the presence of the animal in the artworks, and starts to search about the topic on the web to find [[some interesting results...]]By searching and observing her paints, she notices the presence of the animal in a lot of her works. So she decides to direct her study on this way, and start to navigate on the web to find out [[some interesting results...]]She find some essays and some interesting sites that talk about the argument, though, the content of these resources is not so useful or detailed. By navigating more deeply, she notices a site that seems to be interesting... [[website preview]] [[Go on the website]]
